This article is a presidential memorandum issued by Donald J. Trump on January 23, 2018. The memorandum, titled "Presidential Determination Pursuant to Section 4533(a)(5) of the Defense Production Act of 1950," addresses critical technology item shortfalls affecting thin-wall castings for military applications. Trump determines that these shortfalls are critical to national defense and that without presidential action, the United States defense industrial base cannot adequately provide these capabilities in a timely manner. He authorizes and directs the Secretary of Defense to publish the memorandum in the Federal Register.